It's a ſlander that is upon a ſort of people. As if they would have all things to lie Level, and one to have as much horer as the other; 
A ſlander noed by the Author. 
God forbid we ſhould have ſuch a thought: Let us give honor to thoſe whom God would have honored, and never envy nor grutch at their honor, if God pleaſes to ſend thoſe that are good, I ſay, they may be great Inſtruments of great bleſſings of God to us. But now mark the verie next words that follow in the Eleventh Verſe, They would have a King.

